data.title: Festival Express details
data.meta_description: A rousing record of a little-known, but monumental, moment in rock n roll history.  Set in 1970, Festival Express was a multi-band, multi-day extravaganza that captured the spirit and imagination of a generation and a nation.  (ThinkFilm)
